name: n_two_hop_1
query:
MATCH (c:Customer {contactName: "Maria Anders"})-[:PURCHASED]->(o:Order)
MATCH (o)-[od:ORDERS]->(p:Product)
RETURN o.orderID AS orderID, p.productName AS productName, od.quantity AS quantity
ORDER BY orderID, productName;

name: n_two_hop_2
n_agg_1
n_agg_2
query:
MATCH (c:Customer)-[:PURCHASED]->(o:Order)
RETURN c.contactName AS customer, COUNT(o) AS order_count
ORDER BY order_count DESC, customer
LIMIT 5;

name: n_time_1
query:
MATCH (c:Customer)-[:PURCHASED]->(o:Order)
WHERE o.orderDate STARTS WITH "1997"
RETURN o.orderID AS orderID, o.orderDate AS orderDate, c.contactName AS customer
ORDER BY orderDate, orderID;

name: n_time_2
query:
MATCH (o:Order)
WHERE o.orderDate STARTS WITH "1997"
WITH substring(o.orderDate, 5, 2) AS month
RETURN month, COUNT(*) AS order_count
ORDER BY toInteger(month);

name: n_rec_1
query:
MATCH (p1:Product {productName: "Chai"})<-[:ORDERS]-(o:Order)-[:ORDERS]->(p2:Product)
WHERE p2 <> p1
RETURN p2.productName AS product, COUNT(*) AS freq
ORDER BY freq DESC, product
LIMIT 5;

name: n_rec_2
query:
MATCH (c1:Customer {contactName: "Maria Anders"})-[:PURCHASED]->(:Order)-[:ORDERS]->(p:Product)
MATCH (p)<-[:ORDERS]-(:Order)<-[:PURCHASED]-(c2:Customer)
WHERE c2 <> c1
RETURN c2.contactName AS customer, COUNT(DISTINCT p) AS common_products
ORDER BY common_products DESC, customer;
